OL,3,CTown residents say they can't sit
OL,4,Coutside because of smell and dust from
OL,5,Cfactory
OL,7,FPeople living in Chirk, near Wrexham,
OL,8,Fhave accused wood panel factory
OL,9,FKronospan of "environmental vandalism".
OL,11,FThey claim dust particles from the
OL,12,Fplant are showering their homes and
OL,13,Fcars on a regular basis and the foul
OL,14,Fsmell means they cannot sit outdoors.
OL,16,FThe factory, which employs hundreds of
OL,17,Fpeople, has not commented, but Natural
OL,18,FResources Wales, which regulates the
OL,19,Fsite, say improvements have been made
OL,20,F` but admits there is more to do.
