OL,7,FNestled among the Berwyn mountains and
OL,8,Fthe Ceiriog Valley, Chirk is home to
OL,9,Fthousands of people.
OL,11,FResidents say it is a peaceful place
OL,12,Fto live but others claim the Kronospan
OL,13,Ffactory is blighting their lives.
OL,15,F"I think Kronospan is guilty of
OL,16,Fenvironmental vandalism," said Ian
OL,17,FSykes, who has lived in the village
OL,18,Ffor 48 years.
