OL,7,F"All we want is clean air. We don't
OL,8,Fwant the factory closed down. We just
OL,9,Fwant clean air for the residents of
OL,10,FChirk."
OL,12,FThe retired teacher said dust fibres
OL,13,Fcoming from Kronospan have a huge
OL,14,Fimpact on his life and those around
OL,15,Fhim.
OL,17,F"The odour is so bad we can't sit in
OL,18,Four gardens. We have to come in and
OL,19,Fthe dust covers windowsills, car
OL,20,Fwindscreens, cars, outdoor garden
OL,21,Ftables."
