OL,7,FResidents like Leighton Edwards, a
OL,8,Ffather of four, say they feel
OL,9,Fforgotten.
OL,11,FHe said: "I can't let my kids carry on
OL,12,Fbreathing this in. I'm sick to death
OL,13,Fof it. It's like banging your head
OL,14,Fagainst a brick wall."
OL,16,FFor Amy, who has lived in Chirk most
OL,17,Fof her life, the factory impacts
OL,18,Feveryday life.
