OL,7,FShe said: "We've brought our children
OL,8,Fin from playing outside because of the
OL,9,Fobnoxious smell that we're just
OL,10,Fworried about what they're actually
OL,11,Fbreathing in."
OL,13,FHer young daughter previously wrote to
OL,14,Fthe factory highlighting her fears but
OL,15,Fthe family say she had no response.
OL,17,FThe site has been in the village since
OL,18,Fthe 1970s and has been regulated for
OL,19,Fthe past two years by Natural
OL,20,FResources Wales.
