OL,7,F"One has commented that the Clean Air
OL,8,FAct applies to every part in Wales `
OL,9,Fexcept Chirk it seems. Air monitoring
OL,10,Fequipment that is meant to keep
OL,11,Fresidents safe does not, in fact,
OL,12,Fmonitor microfibres or odours. Chirk
OL,13,Fappears to be a forgotten town when it
OL,14,Fcomes to ensuring residents' safety."
